<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" class="dark">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Accessibility Policy - Stronghold A3 Security Agency</title>
    <!-- [Same Head/CSS as privacy-policy.html] -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;600;700;800&family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root { --gold: #FFD700; --navy: #0A1628; --blue: #3B82F6; }
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; background: radial-gradient(circle at 20% 0%, #002b5c 0%, #001b3d 45%, #000c1f 100%); background-attachment: fixed; min-height: 100vh; color: #fff; }
        body::before { content: ''; position: fixed; top: 50%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%); width: min(80vw, 80vh); height: min(80vw, 80vh); background-image: url('https://fhwhqoiucfxmfsclianh.databasepad.com/storage/v1/object/public/sop-files/public/Stronghold%20Logo.png'); background-size: contain; background-repeat: no-repeat; opacity: 0.03; pointer-events: none; z-index: 0; }
        main, header, footer, nav { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
        h1, h2, h3 { font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; }
        .glass-strong { background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0,43,92,0.55), rgba(0,12,31,0.65)); backdrop-filter: blur(28px); border: 1px solid rgba(255,215,0,0.18); box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.55); border-radius: 1.5rem; padding: 3rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
        header { background: rgba(10, 22, 40, 0.85); backdrop-filter: blur(12px); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2); position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100; }
        .navbar { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding: 1rem 1.5rem; max-width: 1200px; margin: auto; }
        .logo { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem; text-decoration: none; }
        .logo-icon { width: 48px; height: 48px; border-radius: 50%; border: 2px solid var(--blue); overflow: hidden; }
        .logo-icon img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }
        .logo-text { font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.4rem; color: #fff; }
        .logo-subtext { font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--blue); font-weight: 600; }
        .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; list-style: none; }
        .nav-links a { text-decoration: none; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.9rem; padding: 0.5rem 1rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; transition: 0.3s; }
        .nav-links a:hover, .nav-links a.active-page { color: var(--gold); background: rgba(255,215,0,0.1); }
        .hero { padding: 5rem 1.5rem 3rem; text-align: center; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2); }
        .hero h1 { font-size: 2.75rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
        .hero h1 span { color: var(--gold); }
        .hero p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); max-width: 600px; margin: auto; }
        .container { max-width: 1200px; margin: auto; padding: 0 1.5rem; }
        .content-wrapper { margin-top: -2rem; padding-bottom: 4rem; }
        h2 { font-size: 1.6rem; color: var(--gold); margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem; border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(255,215,0,0.2); padding-bottom: 0.5rem; }
        h2 i { color: var(--blue); }
        p, li { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); line-height: 1.8; font-size: 0.95rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
        ul { padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
        li::marker { color: var(--blue); }
        strong { color: #fff; }
        a { color: var(--blue); text-decoration: none; }
        a:hover { color: var(--gold); }
        footer { background: rgba(10, 22, 40, 0.95); border-top: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2); padding: 2rem 1.5rem; text-align: center; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); font-size: 0.85rem; }
        @media (max-width: 768px) { .hero h1 { font-size: 2rem; } .glass-strong { padding: 1.5rem; } .nav-links { display: none; } }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav class="navbar">
            <a href="https://asilvainnovations.github.io/stronghold-a3/" class="logo">
                <div class="logo-icon"><img src="https://fhwhqoiucfxmfsclianh.databasepad.com/storage/v1/object/public/sop-files/public/Stronghold%20Logo.png" alt="Logo"></div>
                <div><div class="logo-text">STRONGHOLD A3</div><div class="logo-subtext">ZERO-LIABILITY SECURITY</div></div>
            </a>
            <ul class="nav-links">
                <li><a href="https://asilvainnovations.github.io/stronghold-a3/">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="https://asilvainnovations.github.io/stronghold-a3/policies.html">Policies</a></li>
                <li><a href="accessibility-policy.html" class="active-page">Accessibility</a></li>
                <li><a href="https://resilient-secure-mobile.deploypad.app/">Staff Portal</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
        <h1>Accessibility <span>Policy</span></h1>
        <p>Ensuring digital inclusivity (WCAG 2.1) and physical security equity for Persons with Disabilities (PWDs) during emergencies.</p>
    </section>

    <main class="content-wrapper">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="glass-strong">
                <h2><i class="fas fa-universal-access"></i> 1. Our Commitment to Inclusivity</h2>
                <p>Stronghold A3 believes that security must be accessible to everyone. Our commitment spans two critical areas: ensuring our digital platforms are usable by individuals with disabilities, and ensuring our physical security and Disaster Risk Reduction and Management (DRRM) protocols actively protect and assist Persons with Disabilities (PWDs) and vulnerable individuals during crises.</p>

                <h2><i class="fas fa-laptop-code"></i> 2. Digital Accessibility (WCAG 2.1 AA)</h2>
                <p>We strive to conform to the <strong>Web Content Accessibility Guidelines (WCAG) 2.1 Level AA</strong> standards. This ensures our website, Client Transparency Portal, and Risk Assessment tools are accessible to users relying on assistive technologies.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Screen Reader Compatibility:</strong> Proper use of semantic HTML, ARIA labels, and alternative text for all security diagrams and icons.</li>
                    <li><strong>Keyboard Navigation:</strong> All interactive elements, including the Risk Assessment Tool and Staff Portal, can be navigated and operated using a keyboard alone.</li>
                    <li><strong>Visual Clarity:</strong> High-contrast "Liquid Glass" UI design, scalable text, and clear color indicators (not relying solely on color to convey risk levels).</li>
                    <li><strong>Continuous Testing:</strong> We regularly audit our digital properties using automated tools and manual testing with assistive devices.</li>
                </ul>

                <h2><i class="fas fa-water"></i> 3. Physical Security & DRRM Inclusivity (RA 10121)</h2>
                <p>In alignment with the <strong>Philippine Disaster Risk Reduction and Management Act (RA 10121)</strong> and the <strong>Magna Carta for Persons with Disabilities (RA 7277)</strong>, our guards are trained to ensure equitable safety during emergencies.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>PWD Evacuation Protocols:</strong> Our site-specific Post Orders include designated PWD evacuation routes and assembly areas. Guards are trained to assist individuals with mobility, visual, or hearing impairments during fire or typhoon evacuations.</li>
                    <li><strong>Accessible Access Control:</strong> Guards are trained to manage access points respectfully, ensuring that security screenings do not discriminate against or unnecessarily delay PWDs or those with medical devices.</li>
                    <li><strong>Emergency Communication:</strong> During crises, our 3-Bridge Communication System ensures that emergency alerts can be conveyed to vulnerable individuals through multiple channels (visual alarms, SMS, direct guard assistance).</li>
                </ul>

                <h2><i class="fas fa-comments"></i> 4. Feedback & Continuous Improvement</h2>
                <p>If you encounter any accessibility barriers on our website, or if you have feedback regarding our physical security protocols for PWDs, please contact us. We are committed to resolving issues promptly.</p>
                <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:compliance@strongholda3.com">compliance@strongholda3.com</a><br>
                <strong>Phone:</strong> 09171370112</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 Stronghold A3 Security Agency. All Rights Reserved. | WCAG 2.1 AA Compliant | RA 10121 DRRM Ready</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
